cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on machine learning and transfer learning using neural networks, which are topics commonly found in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper specifically discusses methods for inductive transfer learning, which is a subfield of machine learning, and compares state-of-the-art methods in weight transfer, deep metric learning, and few-shot learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.AI, followed by cs.CL and cs.NE.
